import React from 'react'
import {Route, Routes} from 'react-router-dom'
import CompA from './CompA'
import CompC from './CompC'
const Router1 = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Routes>
      <Route path='/' element={<CompA />} />
      <Route path='/CompC' element={<CompC />}/>
    </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default Router1
